      <div class=\"txt_t\">朱纪明 副教授 <i></i></div>\n         \n        <div class=\"txt_xq\">\n          <div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_start\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">朱纪明，博士，副教授，博士生导师，主要研究领域包括卫生政策与管理，卫生人力等。</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b>教育经历</b>:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2009-10至2016-09, 牛津大学, 公共健康，博士；全球卫生科学, 硕士（硕博项目都获得全额奖学金）</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2003-09至2007-07, 北京大学, 元培计划实验班（现元培学院），经济学学士</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b>工作经历</b>：</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2018-11至现在，清华大学，万科公共卫生与健康学院；医学院，助理教授，博士生导师</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2019-06至2019-12，世界银行，顾问</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2018-04至2018-10，美国中华医学基金会，顾问及研究专员</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2016-10至2018-03，牛津大学，纳菲尔德医学系，博士后</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b>研究领域：</b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">卫生政策与管理，基础医疗，健康经济学和卫生人力（含护理与医学教育）</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b>承担课题（部分）：</b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1. 比尔及梅琳达·盖茨基金会，提升应急反应能力的整合型医疗健康体系课题，15万美元，在研，主持</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2. 美国中华医学基金会，医院的自我评估提升与推广课题，15万美元，在研，主持</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b>论文著作（部分）：</b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">1. Zhu J*, Ariana P. Provider perspectives on general practice in Henan, China: a mixed-methods study. BMJ Open 2020; 10: e036240.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">2. Wang C, Chen S, Zhu J, Li W. China’s new 4 + 4 medical education programme. The Lancet 2019; 394: 1121–3.</span></p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">3. Zhu J*, Li W, Chen L. Doctors in China: improving quality through modernisation of residency education. The Lancet 2016; 388: 1922–9.</span></p>\n</div>\n                  </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"footer\">\n  <div class=\"wp flex zi3\">\n     <div class=\"logoft flex-v-center\">                <img src=\"../../images/logoft.svg\">\n</div>\n     <div class=\"infoft flex-v-center\">\n       <p class=\"link\">\n<a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1855646458, 80887)\">清华大学主页</a>\n<a href=\"http://intranet.vsph.tsinghua.edu.cn\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1855646458, 80888)\">学院内联网（限内部用户）</a>\n</p>\n       <p class=\"copy\"></p><p>Copyright © 2020 清华大学万科公共卫生与健康学院 &nbsp;All Rights Reserved.</p><p></p>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"codeft\">\n            \t\t\t<img src=\"../../images/code.png\"><p>微信公众号</p>\n\n     </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/lib5.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/anime.min.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/particles.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/u.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/f.js\"></script>\n<!--<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/index.js\"></script>-->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/public.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../js/ny_wow.js\"></script>\n\n\n</body></html>"
